<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>회원가입 - ESS-M.S</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/1.main.css">
    <style>
        /* 회원가입 페이지 전용 스타일 */
        .signup-page-bg {
            background-color: #f4f7f9;
            padding: 60px 0;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 70px);
        }
        .signup-container-wide {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }
        .signup-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .signup-header h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        /* 기기 상세 유형 버튼 스타일 */
        .type-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .type-button.active {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border-color: #007bff;
        }
        .type-button input { display: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="logo" onclick="location.href='1.main.html'" style="cursor:pointer;">ESS-M.S</h1>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="1.main.html">홈</a></li>
                    <li><a href="3.serviceInfo.html">서비스 소개</a></li>
                    <li><a href="2.contact.html">문의게시판</a></li>
                    <li id="auth-menu">
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="login-btn" onclick="openLoginWindow()">로그인</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="signup-page-bg">
        <div class="signup-container-wide">
            <div class="signup-header">
                <h2>회원가입</h2>
                <p>ESS-M.S의 스마트한 에너지 관리를 시작해보세요.</p>
            </div>

            <form action="#" method="post">
                <div class="login-type-tabs" style="margin-bottom: 30px; display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                    <button type="button" class="tab-btn active" onclick="selectType('user')" style="flex:1; padding:12px; cursor:pointer;">개인 회원가입</button>
                    <button type="button" class="tab-btn" onclick="selectType('business')" style="flex:1; padding:12px; cursor:pointer;">기업 회원가입</button>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>아이디</label>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요" required style="width:100%; padding:12px; margin:8px 0; border:1px solid #ddd; border-radius:5px;">
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>비밀번호</label>
                    <input type="password" placeholder="영문, 숫자 포함 8자 이상" required style="width:100%; padding:12px; margin:8px 0; border:1px solid #ddd; border-radius:5px;">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>비밀번호 확인</label>
                    <input type="password" placeholder="비밀번호를 다시 입력하세요" required style="width:100%; padding:12px; margin:8px 0; border:1px solid #ddd; border-radius:5px;">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>이름 / 담당자명</label>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="실명을 입력하세요" required style="width:100%; padding:12px; margin:8px 0; border:1px solid #ddd; border-radius:5px;">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>이메일 주소</label>
                    <input type="email" placeholder="example@ess-ms.com" required style="width:100%; padding:12px; margin:8px 0; border:1px solid #ddd; border-radius:5px;">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="location">설치 지역</label>
                    <select name="location" id="location" required style="width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; margin:8px 0; background-color: #fff;">
                        <option value="" disabled selected>지역을 선택해 주세요</option>
                        <option value="경기도">1. 경기도</option>
                        <option value="강원도">2. 강원도</option>
                        <option value="충청북도">3. 충청북도</option>
                        <option value="충청남도">4. 충청남도</option>
                        <option value="전라북도">5. 전라북도</option>
                        <option value="전라남도">6. 전라남도</option>
                        <option value="경상북도">7. 경상북도</option>
                        <option value="경상남도">8. 경상남도</option>
                        <option value="제주도">9. 제주도</option>
                        <option value="미정">10. 미정</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="device-type">기기 종류</label>
                    <select name="device_type" id="device-type" onchange="updateSubTypes()" required style="width:100%; padding:12px; margin:8px 0; border:1px solid #ddd; border-radius:5px;">
                        <option value="" disabled selected>기기 종류를 선택해 주세요</option>
                        <option value="solar">1. 태양열</option>
                        <option value="hydro">2. 수력</option>
                        <option value="wind">3. 풍력</option>
                        <option value="wave">4. 파력</option>
                        <option value="etc">5. 그외</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <div id="sub-type-section" class="form-group" style="display: none; border: 1px dashed #007bff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; background-color: #f0f7ff; margin-top:10px;">
                    <label style="display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: bold; color: #007bff;">상세 유형을 선택하세요</label>
                    <div id="sub-types-container"></div>
                </div>

                <div id="business-info" style="display:none; margin-top:15px;">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>기업명 (상호명)</label>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="회사명을 입력하세요" style="width:100%; padding:12px; margin:8px 0; border:1px solid #ddd; border-radius:5px;">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>사업자 등록번호</label>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="000-00-00000" style="width:100%; padding:12px; margin:8px 0; border:1px solid #ddd; border-radius:5px;">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn login-submit" style="margin-top:20px; width:100%; padding: 15px; background:#007bff; color:white; border:none; border-radius:5px; font-weight:bold; cursor:pointer;">회원가입 완료</button>
            </form>

            <div class="login-footer" style="text-align:center; margin-top:20px;">
                <p>이미 계정이 있으신가요? <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="openLoginWindow()" style="color:#007bff; text-decoration:none;">로그인하기</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container footer-content">
            <div class="footer-info">
                <h2 class="footer-logo">ESS-M.S</h2>
                <p>스마트 에너지 모니터링 시스템 전문 기업</p>
                <address>
                    부산광역시 범내골 kh 학원 <br>
                    대표전화: 051-123-4567 | 이메일: info@ess-ms.com
                </address>
                <p class="copyright">&copy; 2026 ESS-Monitoring System. All Rights Reserved.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-links">
                <h4>Quick Links</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="1.main.html">홈</a></li>
                    <li><a href="3.serviceInfo.html">서비스 소개</a></li>
                    <li><a href="2.contact.html">문의게시판</a></li>
                    <li><a href="7.newsupdate.html">최신 정보</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-sns">
                <h4>Follow Us</h4>
                <div class="sns-icons">
                    <span>Blog</span>
                    <span>LinkedIn</span>
                    <span>Youtube</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="js/6.signup.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
